mony from people who had been present with Sara(h) when some of the fires started).<br><br>I can't remember in precise terms what the actual verdict was, however I think the trial found that Sara(h) WAS the probable cause of the fires, but that she could not be found guilty of having started them deliberately, or with intent.  In other words, she was the unwilling, unknowing cause of the fires!<br><br>Anyway, I can't remember where I read this article, and I haven't (so far) been able to find out anything more by searching on the web.<br><br>Does anyone know anything about this case?  I may have got her first name completely wrong - I think it was Sara or Sarah - but I'm 99% positive that her surname was 'Compton'.  <br><br>Does anyone feel like doing some research - I seem to have run into lots of dead ends with this! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START |I --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tired.gif ALT="|I"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>Paul<br>Powys/ UK<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/upaulbst.showPublicProfile?language=EN>paulbst</A> at: 7/21/01 12:37:51 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/udotzap.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DOTZAP</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://members.aol.com/maidenntheshaden/btrfly6.gif height=35 width=35 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Angelight</span><br>  Posts: 2995<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/20/01 5:53:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm51.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=362.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/maidenntheshaden/maxmouse.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60>